<block tt:if="{{isShow}}"><view data-event-opts="{{[['touchmove',[['catchTouchMove',['$event']]]]]}}" class="login-tips-block" catchtouchmove="__e"><view class="login-tips border-radius20"><view class="icon-top-play"><image src="{{$root.m0}}" mode></image></view><view class="h4">授权获取手机号</view><view class="h5"><text>为了完整体验,需要您的授权</text><text>授权后可享受更多优质服务</text></view><button class="{{(('login-btn')+' '+(isAllAngle?'border-radius-style-all-arg':'border-radius-style-half-arg'))}}" style="{{'background:'+(configInfo.web_site_color)+';'}}" open-type="getPhoneNumber" data-event-opts="{{[['getphonenumber',[['wxGetTelFn',['$event']]]]]}}" bindgetphonenumber="__e">确认授权</button><text data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['closeFn',['$event']]]]]}}" class="say-no" style="{{'color:'+(configInfo.web_site_color)+';'}}" bindtap="__e">关闭</text></view></view></block>